# Weather App

This is a simple Weather Application developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The application allows users to check real-time weather information by entering a city name. It fetches weather data from a weather API and displays temperature, weather condition, humidity, and wind speed.

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Weather API

## Features
- Search weather by city name
- Displays temperature and weather condition
- Shows humidity and wind speed
- Responsive and user-friendly interface

## How It Works
1. User enters a city name.
2. JavaScript sends a request to the weather API.
3. Weather data is fetched and displayed dynamically on the webpage.

## Tools Used
- VS Code
- Web Browser

## Purpose
To practice API integration and build an interactive frontend application using JavaScript.
